President Donald J. Trump has announced his intent to nominate several individuals for key positions in his administration. James Donovan will serve as Deputy Secretary of the Treasury. J. Christopher Giancarlo will serve as Chairman of the Commodity Futures Trading Commission. Eric D. Hargan will serve as Deputy Secretary of Health and Human Services. Adam Lerrick will serve as Deputy Under Secretary of the Treasury for International Finance. Andrew K. "Drew" Maloney will serve as Deputy Under Secretary of the Treasury for Legislative Affairs. David Malpass will serve as Under Secretary of the Treasury for International Affairs. Sigal Mandelker will serve as Under Secretary of the Treasury for Terrorism and Financial Intelligence. Brent James McIntosh will serve as General Counsel for the Department of the Treasury.